Transfer Funds to Own Account Service Process (Unmanaged Package)

The Transfer Funds to Own Account service process allows your customers to transfer funds between their financial accounts that are either within the same bank or with a different bank.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled

Setup and Configuration of the Transfer Funds to Own Account Service Process
Use the Service Process Studio to enable the Transfer Funds to Own Account service process to give your agents an easy-to-follow process for capturing a funds transfer request.

Submit a Request to Transfer Funds Between Accounts
Your service agents can capture and submit a request for fund transfer through the Transfer Funds to Own Account OmniScript. A case is then created in Salesforce.
title: Transfer Funds Service Process in Financial Services Cloud
